#: ../../source/api/constituency_assigner.rst:2
msgid "ConstituencyAssigner"
msgstr "ConstituencyAssigner"

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:1 of
msgid "Assigns constituencies to parties based on relative importance."
msgstr "Weist Parteien Wahlkreise basierend auf relativer Bedeutung zu."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:3 of
msgid ""
"This is the third of three evaluation steps performed after a finished "
"election. It can be used standalone or as part of "
":class:`~ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator`."
msgstr ""
"Dies ist der dritte von drei Auswertungsschritten nach einer "
"abgeschlossenen Wahl. Er kann eigenständig oder als Teil des "
":class:`~ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator` verwendet werden."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:6 of
msgid ""
"Relative importance is derived from the vote distribution across "
"constituencies via "
":class:`~ipres.vote_matrix_analyzer.VoteMatrixAnalyzer`. The assignment "
"algorithm is chosen via ``constituency_allocation_method``."
msgstr ""
"Die relative Bedeutung wird aus der Stimmenverteilung über Wahlkreise "
"mithilfe des :class:`~ipres.vote_matrix_analyzer.VoteMatrixAnalyzer` "
"abgeleitet. Der Zuweisungsalgorithmus wird über "
"``constituency_allocation_method`` gewählt."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:10 of
msgid ""
"When the election's ``constituency_representation`` is "
"``GOVERNING_MAJORITY``, only votes for the winning parties are used to "
"compute importance. The mode is derived automatically from "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_representation`` inside "
":meth:`run`."
msgstr ""
"Wenn ``constituency_representation`` der Wahl ``GOVERNING_MAJORITY`` ist, "
"werden zur Berechnung der Bedeutung nur Stimmen für die Gewinnerparteien "
"verwendet. Der Modus wird innerhalb von :meth:`run` automatisch aus "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_representation`` abgeleitet."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_assigner.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parameter"

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:17 of
msgid ""
"Algorithm used to assign constituencies. When ``None`` (default), the "
"value is inherited from "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_allocation_method``."
msgstr ""
"Algorithmus zur Zuweisung von Wahlkreisen. Bei ``None`` (Standard) wird "
"der Wert aus "
"``election.electionConfig.constituency_allocation_method`` übernommen."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner of
msgid "type"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:21 of
msgid "ipres.allocation.ConstituencyAllocationMethod | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:25 of
msgid "Pre-built NumPy random generator. Takes precedence over ``seed``."
msgstr "Vorgefertigter NumPy-Zufallsgenerator. Hat Vorrang vor ``seed``."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:27 of
msgid "numpy.random._generator.Generator | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:31 of
msgid ""
"Seed for the random generator used in allocation. When ``None`` "
"(default), the value is inherited from ``election.electionConfig.seed``."
msgstr ""
"Seed für den bei der Zuweisung verwendeten Zufallsgenerator. Bei ``None`` "
"(Standard) wird der Wert aus ``election.electionConfig.seed`` übernommen."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner:34 of
msgid "int | None"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner.run:1 of
msgid ""
"Assign constituencies to parties and return a constituency-to-party "
"mapping."
msgstr ""
"Weist Parteien Wahlkreise zu und gibt eine Zuordnung von Wahlkreis zu "
"Partei zurück."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner.run:3 of
msgid "A finished election with a winner."
msgstr "Eine abgeschlossene Wahl mit einem Sieger."

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner.run:4 of
msgid ""
"Constituency counts per party as returned by "
":class:`~ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer`."
msgstr ""
"Wahlkreisanzahl pro Partei, wie von "
":class:`~ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer` "
"zurückgegeben."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_assigner.rst
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "Rückgabewert"

#: ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner.run:7 of
msgid "Dictionary mapping each constituency name to the party it represents."
msgstr "Wörterbuch, das jeden Wahlkreisnamen der Partei zuordnet, die ihn vertritt."

#: ../../source/api/constituency_assigner.rst
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "Rückgabetyp"
